Using k-Means to Cluster Tweets {.title .toc-ignore}
===============================

#### Jana Osea and Evan Quan {.author}

#### November 25, 2020 {.date}

Dataset Previews
----------------

to November 25, 2020 using \\(n=400\\) tweets.

k-Means Clustering
------------------

We plotted the cluster plots with \\(k=2,3,4,5\\) clusters
correspondingly.
![](data:image/png;base64,)

We choose \\(k=2\\) as our chosen number of clusters and we will now
analyze.
